---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Knowledge Base" description="Upload documents and FAQs to ground AI reply drafts in your product's actual positioning.">
  <h1>Knowledge Base</h1>

  <p style="margin-top: 16px;">
    The knowledge base stores documents — FAQs, positioning guides, feature descriptions, case studies —
    that are used as RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) context when drafting AI replies.
    This ensures replies reference your product's actual capabilities rather than hallucinated claims.
  </p>

  <h2>How It Works</h2>

  <ol>
    <li>You upload a document via the dashboard or API.</li>
    <li>LeadEcho chunks the content and generates 1024-dim embeddings via Voyage AI.</li>
    <li>Embeddings are stored in pgvector alongside the text chunks.</li>
    <li>When drafting a reply, the system retrieves the top 3 most relevant chunks (up to 500 chars each).</li>
    <li>These chunks are injected into the LLM prompt as context.</li>
  </ol>

  <blockquote>
    <p>
      RAG retrieval requires a <code>VOYAGE_API_KEY</code>. Without it, reply drafts are generated
      without knowledge base context.
    </p>
  </blockquote>

  <h2>Uploading Documents</h2>

  <h3>Via Dashboard</h3>

  <p>
    Navigate to <strong>Knowledge Base</strong> in the sidebar → click <strong>Add Document</strong>.
    Paste or type the content directly — markdown is supported.
  </p>

  <h3>Via API</h3>

  <pre><code>POST /api/v1/documents
Authorization: Bearer &lt;jwt&gt;
Content-Type: application/json

&#123;
  "title": "LeadEcho Feature Overview",
  "content": "# LeadEcho\n\nLeadEcho monitors 7 social platforms...",
  "content_type": "markdown",
  "source_url": "https://leadecho.app/features"
&#125;</code></pre>

  <h3>Response</h3>

  <pre><code>&#123;
  "id": "doc_01hx...",
  "title": "LeadEcho Feature Overview",
  "content_type": "markdown",
  "source_url": "https://leadecho.app/features",
  "chunk_count": 4,
  "created_at": "2025-03-01T10:00:00Z"
&#125;</code></pre>

  <h2>Document Schema</h2>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Field</th>
        <th>Type</th>
        <th>Required</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><code>title</code></td>
        <td>string</td>
        <td>Yes</td>
        <td>Human-readable title shown in the dashboard</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>content</code></td>
        <td>string</td>
        <td>Yes</td>
        <td>Full document text (markdown supported)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>content_type</code></td>
        <td>enum</td>
        <td>No</td>
        <td><code>markdown</code> (default), <code>text</code></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>source_url</code></td>
        <td>string</td>
        <td>No</td>
        <td>Original URL if the document was scraped from a web page</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>What to Upload</h2>

  <p>Documents that improve reply quality the most:</p>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Product FAQ</strong> — common questions and concise answers</li>
    <li><strong>Positioning guide</strong> — how to describe your product vs competitors</li>
    <li><strong>Feature list</strong> — specific capabilities with brief descriptions</li>
    <li><strong>Case studies</strong> — real customer outcomes in 2–3 sentences each</li>
    <li><strong>Pricing explainer</strong> — what's included at each tier</li>
    <li><strong>Founder story</strong> — "why we built this" for authentic replies</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Chunking Behavior</h2>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Parameter</th>
        <th>Value</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>Chunk size</td>
        <td>~500 characters</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Overlap</td>
        <td>50 characters (preserves context at boundaries)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Split strategy</td>
        <td>Paragraph-first, then sentence boundaries</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Embedding model</td>
        <td><code>voyage-3-lite</code> (1024 dims)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Retrieval top-k</td>
        <td>3 chunks per reply draft</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>API Reference</h2>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Method</th>
        <th>Path</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><code>GET</code></td>
        <td><code>/api/v1/documents</code></td>
        <td>List all documents</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>POST</code></td>
        <td><code>/api/v1/documents</code></td>
        <td>Create and embed a document</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>GET</code></td>
        <td><code>/api/v1/documents/&#123;id&#125;</code></td>
        <td>Get a single document</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>PUT</code></td>
        <td><code>/api/v1/documents/&#123;id&#125;</code></td>
        <td>Update document content (re-embeds)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>DELETE</code></td>
        <td><code>/api/v1/documents/&#123;id&#125;</code></td>
        <td>Delete document and its embeddings</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</DocsLayout>
